OOC: Alright I think I've had enough of this feud.  For the moment I'm going 
to assume that Tankor is telling the truth about missing the posts.  It 
happens.  If you feel like yelling at each other, so be it.  Keep it off the 
boards.  As for his signature, "Death to the nWo."  I'm not going to stop 
that.  It's not like the nWo doesn't put insulting things in their signatures 
too.  Uhoh, almost quoted a stupid cliche (I know it needs an accent 
alright).  Time for me to stop writing.  This matter is closed until 
something else goes wrong.
